data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF on this Harder Hall home with split floor plan boasting over 1800 living square feet located on a corner lot.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a remodeled kitchen and bath as of 2017.  Kitchen contains updated appliances, countertops and flooring.  There is plenty of room for entertaining in this home, from the large open Great Room to the Formal Dining Space, Kitchen and Breakfast Bar, Casual Dining Space, and back porch; surely, everyone will have a place to relax.  The large master has two separate closets, a corner tub, and step-in shower. Each of the other bedrooms are on the separate end of the home, and share the guest bath with shower/tub.  Laundry is in a private room and contains additional pantry space, cabinets, and laundry sink.  The owner is leaving both the washer and dryer on pedestals.  In addition, the home features an irrigation system and central security system.  Please give at least 1 hr notice to show.
